{
 "translations": [
  {
   "offset": 9,
   "len": 51,
   "en": "a dark, bearded man dressed in flowing white robes.",
   "zh": "身穿白袍、蓄著鬍鬚的黝黑男子。",
   "note": "DESC"
  },
  {
   "offset": 64,
   "len": 64,
   "en": "\"Greetings, mighty Avatar. For what hast thou come to my place?\"",
   "zh": "「問候，偉大的聖者。汝前來敝處，所為何事？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 178,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"I am Rudyom.\"",
   "zh": "「吾乃魯迪奧姆。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 208,
   "len": 55,
   "en": "\"I sell magic @books and @reagents, and teach @spells.\"",
   "zh": "「吾販售魔法@書卷及@施法材料，並傳授@法術。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 273,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"May peace follow thee, Avatar.\"",
   "zh": "「願平安伴隨汝，聖者。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 310,
   "len": 29,
   "en": "\"Of that I will say nothing.\"",
   "zh": "「此事吾無可奉告。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 352,
   "len": 30,
   "en": "\"My shop is closed right now.\"",
   "zh": "「店鋪目前關閉。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 447,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"But thou hast not a spell@book!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝尚無法術@書卷！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 607,
   "len": 35,
   "en": "\"But none of you has a spell@book!\"",
   "zh": "「但你們沒有一人持有法術@書卷！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 679,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「你們哪位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 811,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"In which Circle does $Y wish to study?\" ",
   "zh": "「$Y希望習學第幾階法術？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 875,
   "len": 51,
   "en": "\"As everybody knows, there are only eight circles.\"",
   "zh": "「眾所周知，法術共有八階。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 942,
   "len": 52,
   "en": "\"I sense that $Y is only ready for the #1$1 Circle.\"",
   "zh": "「吾感知到$Y目前只宜修習第#1$1階。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 997,
   "len": 40,
   "en": "\"But such matters are not my concern...\"",
   "zh": "「但此類事吾不置喙……」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1075,
   "len": 34,
   "en": "\"I have no spells of that circle.\"",
   "zh": "「吾無此階法術。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1187,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "\"Which of these?\" ",
   "zh": "「要哪一項？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1221,
   "len": 42,
   "en": "\"Perhaps $Y is not ready for this circle.\"",
   "zh": "「或許$Y尚未準備好修習此階。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1305,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"$Y lacks the #5 gold required.\"",
   "zh": "「$Y金幣不足，需#5枚。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
